INSERT INTO `benefit_program` VALUES (21,_binary '\0','Antigua and Barbuda passport holders enjoy visa-free access to 151 countries, including Hong Kong, Singapore, the UK, and Europe\'s Schengen Area','Ease of Travel',22),(22,_binary '\0','No personal income, inheritance, or capital gains tax. Citizens are also free from paying taxes on dividends, interests, or royalties from around the world','Tax Benefits',22),(23,_binary '\0','Spouses, children below 30,  parents and grandparents over 55, unmarried siblings can also be included','Inclusive Family Options',22),(24,_binary '\0','Antigua and Barbuda is an appealing destination for owning a second home, as it offers a valuable safety net, ensuring peace of mind for investors and their families','Quality of Life',22),(25,_binary '\0','Visa-free passport to 145 countries, including all EU Schengen countries, Singapore, and Hong Kong. Citizens of Dominica can access a 10-year visa for travel to the United States','Ease of Travel',24),(26,_binary '\0','Dominica citizens, including those through investment, enjoy tax exemptions on global dividends, interest, and royalties. The country is also tax-free for income, capital gains, and inheritance','Taxation Benefits',24),(27,_binary '\0','No restrictions on dual citizenship in Dominica. This flexibility facilitates international mobility and opportunities for those seeking to acquire Dominican citizenship while maintaining ties to their home country','Dual Citizenship',24),(28,_binary '\0','Spouses, children below 30, parents and grandparents over 65, as well as dependents can also be included after citizenship has been granted to the main applicant','Inclusive Family Options',24),(29,_binary '\0','Visa-free passport to 65 countries, including Hong Kong and Malaysia. 46 states offer visa-on-arrival while Australia, Sri Lanka, and Seychelles require electronic authorisation in advance','Visa-free or Visa-on-arrival Access',25),(30,_binary '\0','Egypt has created nine free zones where investors can launch a business and pay no corporate income tax','Tax Benefits',25),(31,_binary '\0','Program participants can reclaim their investments five years after receiving a passport by selling a business, closing a deposit in an Egyptian bank, or selling real estate','Returnable Investments',25),(32,_binary '\0','Visa-free access to 157 countries, including all EU Schengen countries, Singapore, and Hong Kong. Additionally, citizens enjoy a 10-year U.S. visa, easing access to otherwise challenging travel permissions','Ease of Travel',26),(33,_binary '\0','An equitable tax system, wherein passport holders are exempt from global income, inheritance and gift taxes','Taxation Benefits',26),(34,_binary '\0','Holders of St. Kitts & Nevis passports can register their companies in the country, avoiding issues such as foreign exchange complications and other common challenges encountered by international businesses','Business Opportunities',26),(35,_binary '\0','Spouses, children below 26, parents and grandparents over 65, as well as dependents can also be included after citizenship has been granted to the main applicant','Inclusive Family Options',26),(36,_binary '\0','St. Lucia passport holders can enjoy visa-free travel to 147 countries, including Hong Kong, Singapore, the UK, and the Schengen zone. They also receive a 10-year visa to the US, allowing them to spend up to 6 months there each year','Travel Opportunities',27),(37,_binary '\0','If you start a company in St. Lucia, it can make it simpler for business owners to use international banks, handle foreign currency transactions, and maybe even pay fewer taxes','International Business Benefits',27),(38,_binary '\0','In the same way that international businesses registered in St. Lucia will experience lower taxes, individuals with a St. Lucia passport also experience lighter tax burdens. In St. Lucia, there are no taxes on income, inheritance, or capital gains','Favorable Taxation Policies',27),(39,_binary '\0','Visa-free access to 146 countries, including the UK, the Schengen States, Singapore and Hong Kong. Also, the biggest advantage of Grenada citizenship is the E-2 visa for the United States, allowing applicants to live and work there. To qualify, applicants must invest at least USD 100,000 by establishing or buying a business in the United States','Ease of Travel',28),(40,_binary '\0','Grenada doesnt tax individuals on global income, dividends, interest, or royalties from another country. There are no taxes on inheritance tax, capital gains tax and stamp duty','Tax Optimization',28),(41,_binary '\0','Spouses, children and parents may acquire citizenship alongside investors. The status is inherited by the citizens children','Inclusive Family Options',28),(42,_binary '\0','The maltese passport is the 9th strongest passport in the world, offering visa-free access to 185 countries. The list includes the UK, the USA, Japan, Singapore and Hong Kong','Visa-Free Travel',29),(43,_binary '\0','Malta citizens can start a business in any EU country, allowing business owners to expand to the international market','Business Opportunities',29),(44,_binary '\0','Maltese citizenship by investment program ensures a lifelong status, granting individuals the full rights to live, work, and own property in Malta','Lifelong Maltese Citizenship',29),(45,_binary '\0','Once investors obtain Austrian citizenship, they are exempt from taxes in the country unless they choose to reside there','Tax Exemption',30),(46,_binary '\0','An Austrian citizenship allows investors to live and work anywhere within the European Union without restrictions. Additionally, it enables residency in Switzerland, which is very popular for its tax-advantaged residence','No Requirements to Live in Austria',30),(47,_binary '\0','Investors can open an account in an Austrian bank in any currency, while the information on accounts and personal data remain entirely confidential','Reliable Banking System',30),(48,