eir invested funds','Returnable Investments',33),(57,_binary '\0','The Greece Golden Visa allows investors and their families to reside in Greece full time, providing a pathway to citizenship. After 5 years of residency, investors can apply for permanent residency, followed by citizenship eligibility in another 2 years','Path to EU Citizenship',33),(58,_binary '\0','Investors benefit from a favorable tax regime with no personal income, capital, net worth, or withholding tax','Tax Optimization',34),(59,_binary '\0','Holders of the Esaad Privilege Card can enjoy exclusive offers, bonuses, and discounts of up to 70% in government agencies, service companies, shops, medical clinics, language schools, and travel companies','Free Esaad Privilege Card ',34),(60,_binary '\0','Golden Visa holders can easily travel in and out of the UAE. The Golden Visa is a multiple-entry visa, allowing holders to reenter several times without applying for a new visa','Travel Benefits',34),(61,_binary '\0','Investors with a residence permit can open accounts in the UAE banks in dollars, euros, dirhams and other currencies','Opening a Bank Account in The UAE',34),(62,_binary '\0','Investors enjoy a favorable tax system with no taxes on global income and inheritance, along with low property and income tax rates. The corporate tax is among the lowest in Europe','Tax Optimization',35),(63,_binary '\0','Investors have the option to purchase shares in local businesses, establish their own companies, or transfer existing companies to the island\'s jurisdiction','Business Opportunities',35),(64,_binary '\0','Residents in Cyprus can improve their quality of life, access education in local schools and universities, and seek medical assistance from local facilities','High Quality of Life',35),(65,_binary '\0','EB-5 visa holders can open local bank accounts in dollars, euros and other currencies and they can gain access to extensive US banking services','Opening Bank Accounts in the USA',36),(66,_binary '\0','After five years of legal residence, investors can apply for citizenship. The US passport allows visa-free travel to over 180 countries','Opportunity to Obtain US Citizenship',36),(67,_binary '\0','High levels of safety and security, excellent education opportunities, and robust healthcare options','Secured Living',36),(68,_binary '\0','151 countries, including Hong Kong, Singapore, the UK, and Europe\'s Schengen Area','Visa-Free Travel',23),(69,_binary '\0','No personal income, inheritance, or capital gains tax','Tax Benefits',23),(70,_binary '\0','spouse, children below 30, parents and grandparents (above 55 years old), and unmarried siblings','Family Citizenship Options',23),(71,_binary '\0','Antigua and Barbuda is an appealing destination for a second home, as it offers a valuable safety net, ensuring peace of mind for investors and their families','Quality of Life',23);
