INSERT INTO `blog` VALUES (1,'TN','2024-07-04 11:33:19.140000','At Growbal, we\'ve always understood the impact our platform can have, not just on businesses and freelancers, but on communities as a whole. With the launch of our Social Impact Hub, we\'re taking our commitment to positive change to the next level. The hub is a place where the Growbal community, nonprofit organizations, and partners can come together to explore and engage with our social impact programs and partnerships. It\'s a space designed to showcase our ongoing initiatives, highlight impactful partnerships, and provide resources for social impact organizations leading change. The core mission of Growbal\'s social impact work is to make way for community breakthroughs by nurturing equity, well-being, and impact. More specifically, the areas we build programming and partnerships around are focused on: Fostering economic opportunity, supporting freelancer well-being, and amplifying the impact of nonprofit organizations.',_binary '\0',_binary '','Africa','We Launcheed Social Impact Hub',11,1,'2024-03-21 11:30:53.914000','At Growbal, we\'ve always understood the impact our platform can have, not just on businesses and freelancers, but on communities as a whole. With the launch of our Social Impact Hub, we\'re taking our commitment to positive change to the next level.','SOCIAL IMPACT','Michelle Baltrusitis',1,NULL),(2,'string','2024-07-04 12:59:31.042000','<p>write your blog details</p>',_binary '\0',_binary '','string','testy',2495,1,'2024-07-04 12:01:03.798000','tsty','#test','thamer',1,NULL),(3,'string','2024-07-04 13:03:31.484000','<ul><li>55120&nbsp;</li><li>201151*561514</li><li>5558451251845</li></ul>',_binary '\0',_binary '','string','testyy',2499,1,'2024-07-04 12:05:04.241000','testyy','#tag','thamer',1,NULL),(4,'string','2024-07-04 13:10:06.464000','<p>write your blog details</p>',_binary '\0',_binary '','string','testy',2500,1,'2024-07-04 12:11:39.231000','Short description','Tag','testy ',1,NULL),(5,'string','2024-07-04 13:12:31.673000','<p>write your blog details</p>',_binary '',_binary '\0','string','testy',2501,1,'2024-07-04 12:14:04.440000','Short description','Tag','testy ',1,NULL),(6,'TN','2024-07-05 09:17:20.369000','TEST LONGER DESCRIPTION',_binary '',_binary '\0','Africa','TEST TITLE',18,1,'2024-07-05 09:16:16.823000','TEST SHORT DESCRIPTION','TEST TAG','TEST WRITER',1,NULL),(7,'string','2024-07-05 10:17:46.626000','<ol><li>test 1</li><li>test 2</li><br></ol>',_binary '',_binary '\0','string','string',1,1,'2024-07-05 13:09:32.470000','string','Changed','string',1,NULL),(8,'string','2024-07-08 09:41:55.590000','<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The United Arab Emirates (UAE) has established a comprehensive legal framework specifically designed to support and regulate family-owned businesses. This legislation, Federal Decree Law No. 37 of 2022 Concerning Family Businesses (the \"Law\"), came into effect in January 2023.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Rationale and Objectives</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Law reflects the UAE government\'s recognition of family businesses as critical drivers of the national economy. These businesses generate significant employment opportunities and contribute to economic activity through their supply chains. The Law aims to achieve several key objectives:</span></strong></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Establish a Clear Legal Framework:</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Provide a comprehensive legal structure governing ownership, governance, and succession planning for family businesses in the UAE.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ensure Business Continuity:</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Facilitate the smooth transfer of a family business from one generation to the next, promoting long-term sustainability.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Strengthen the Private Sector:</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Enhance the role of family businesses in driving economic growth and social development in the UAE.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Attract Investment:</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Make the UAE a more attractive investment destination for family offices and family-owned businesses from around the world.</span></strong></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Defining a Family Business</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Under the Law, a \"Family Business\" is a company established in accordance with the UAE Companies Law, with a majority of shares or ownership interests held by members of a single family.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Scope of Application</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Law applies to a broad range of family businesses operating within the UAE, including:</span></strong></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Existing family businesses at the time of the Law\'s enactment.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Newly established family businesses.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Family businesses located within free zones.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Family businesses operating in individual emirates, except where local legislation already governs such businesses (in which case, the Law may apply to non-regulated areas).</span></strong></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Law excludes joint-stock companies and partnerships from its scope.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Registration Requirements</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Family businesses are required to register with a unified Family Business Register established by the Ministry of Economy. This registration process may be coordinated with relevant local authorities depending on the Emirate or free zone where the business operates.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Family Charter</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">In addition to the standard Memorandum of Association (MoA), family businesses must create a Family Charter. This document outlines the governance structure for managing family involvement in the business and establishes guidelines for the family\'s relationship with the company. The Family Charter must be deposited within the Register. In the event of a conflict between the MoA and the Family Charter, the MoA provisions prevail.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Share Classes</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Law allows family businesses to issue two distinct classes of shares:</span></strong></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Share (A):</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Provides voting rights and entitlement to company profits.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans Symbols\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Share (B):</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Grants exclusive rights to profits without voting privileges.</span></strong></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Law allows a family business, with majority shareholder approval, to repurchase up to 30% of its own share capital in specific situations, such as capital reduction or purchasing shares from a departing member.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Management Structure</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The MoA designates the management structure for a family business. In the absence of such provisions, partners holding at least 51% of the shares can appoint a director. Directors can be individuals or legal entities, although at least one director must be a natural person if there\'s more than one appointed.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">For family businesses established as limited liability companies, the MoA may specify the formation of a Board of Directors (BOD). The MoA will govern the rules, composition, and powers of the BOD, including terms of membership, compensation, appointment/removal procedures, and decision-making mechanisms. The BOD will appoint a Chairperson who acts as the representative but does not have a casting vote.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Dispute Resolution</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Law empowers family businesses to choose their preferred method for resolving disputes. Options include a dedicated Family Business Dispute Resolution Committee in each Emirate, the courts within financial free zones, or arbitration.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Incentives and Support</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Law creates a supportive environment for family businesses and family offices to establish themselves in the UAE. Additionally, family businesses may be eligible for occasional incentives and concessions at the discretion of the UAE Cabinet.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Dubai Centre for Family Businesses</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The Dubai Chamber of Commerce launched the Dubai Centre for Family Businesses (the \"Centre\") in May 2023. The Centre aims to promote the growth and sustainability of family businesses within the Emirate. It offers educational programs like the Governance Series, focusing on key issues impacting family business success. The Centre recently announced a new Family Business Advisory Certificate program in partnership with the Family Firm Institute (FFI) to equip family businesses with valuable knowledge and tools.</span></strong></p><p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Disclaimer:</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> This article provides general information and does not constitute legal advice. To seek personalized legal counsel tailored to your specific circumstances, Growbal encourages you to contact legal experts.</span></strong></p>',_binary '',_binary '\0','string','The UAE\'s New Framework for Family Businesses',2508,1,'2024-07-08 09:33:43.353000','The United Arab Emirates (UAE) has established a comprehensive legal framework specifically designed to support and regulate family-owned businesses. This legislation, Federal Decree Law No. 37 of 2022 Concerning Family Businesses (the \"Law\"), came into e','Family Business','OHLLP',2507,NULL),(9,'string','2024-07-08 12:44:32.612000','<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The United Arab Emirates (UAE) has established a comprehensive legal framework specifically designed to support and regulate family-owned businesses. This legislation, Federal Decree Law No. 37 of 2022 Concerning Family Businesses (the \"Law\"), came into effect in January 2023.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Rationale and Objectives</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Law reflects the UAE government\'s recognition of family businesses as critical drivers of the national economy. These businesses generate significant employment opportunities and contribute to economic activity through their supply chains. The Law aims to achieve several key objectives:</span></strong></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 2rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stro