m around the world.</span></strong></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Defining a Family Business</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Under the Law, a \"Family Business\" is a company established in accordance with the UAE Companies Law, with a majority of shares or ownership interests held by members of a single family.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Scope of Application</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Law applies to a broad range of family businesses operating within the UAE, including:</span></strong></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 2rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; padding-inline-start: 48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Existing family businesses at the time of the Law\'s enactment.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 0pt 0px; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e