-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Law allows a family business, with majority shareholder approval, to repurchase up to 30% of its own share capital in specific situations, such as capital reduction or purchasing shares from a departing member.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Management Structure</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;