variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Family businesses are required to register with a unified Family Business Register established by the Ministry of Economy. This registration process may be coordinated with relevant local authorities depending on the Emirate or free zone where the business operates.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Family Charter</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In addition to the standard Memorandum of Association (MoA), family businesses must create a Family Charter. This document outlines the governance structure for managing family involvement in the business and establishes guidelines for the family\'s relationship with the company. The Family Charter must be deposited within the Register. In the event of a conflict between the MoA and the Family Charter, the MoA provisions prevail.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Share Classes</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Law