nt-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Provides voting rights and entitlement to company profits.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 0pt 0px 14pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Share (B):</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Grants exclusive rights to profits without voting privileges.</span></strong></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Law allows a family business, with majority shareholder approval, to repurchase up to 30% of its own share capital in specific situations, such as capital reduction or purchasing shares from a departing member.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Management Structure</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The MoA designates the management structure for a family business. In the absence of such provisions, partners holding at least 51% of the shares can appoint a director. Directors can be individuals or legal entities, although at least one director must be a natural person if there\'s more than one appointed.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For family businesses established as limited liability companies, the MoA may specify the formation of a Board of Directors (BOD). The MoA will govern the rules, composition, and powers of the BOD, including terms of membership, compensation, appointment/removal procedures, and decision-making mechanisms. The BOD will appoint a Chairperson who acts as the representative but does not have a casting vote.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Dispute Resolution</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Law empowers family businesses to choose their preferred method for resolving disputes. Options include a dedicated Family Business Dispute Resolution Committee in each Emirate, the courts within financial free zones, or arbitration.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Incentives and Support</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Law creates a supportive environment for family businesses and family offices to establish themselves in the UAE. Additionally, family businesses may be eligible for occasional incentives and concessions at the discretion of the UAE Cabinet.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Dubai Centre for Family Businesses</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Dubai Chamber of Commerce launched the Dubai Centre for Family Businesses (the \"Centre\") in May 2023. The Centre aims to promote the growth and sustainability of family businesses within the Emirate. It offers educational programs like the Governance Series, focusing on key issues impacting family business success. The Centre recently announced a new Family Business Advisory Certificate program in partnership with the Family Firm Institute (FFI) to equip family businesses with valuable knowledge and tools.</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Disclaimer:</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth