EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Introduced\n        in 2017, foundations have become a popular choice for:</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Wealth Structuring and Succession\n            Planning:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> Facilitating the transfer of wealth\n        across generations.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Asset Protection:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> Providing a layer of security\n        against creditors, governments, or other claimants.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 19px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Long-Term Asset Management:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> Holding income-generating assets\n        such as businesses or real estate portfolios.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Available Jurisdictions</span></strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Foundations\n        can be established in three key jurisdictions within the UAE:</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Dubai International Financial Centre\n            (DIFC):</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> Governed by DIFC Foundations Law\n        No. 3 of 2018.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Abu Dhabi Global Market (ADGM):</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> Governed by Foundations Regulations\n        2017.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 19px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ras Al Khaimah International\n            Corporate Centre (RAKICC):</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">\n        Governed by RAK ICC Foundations Regulations 2019.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">While\n        the regulations are largely similar, there are some key differences to\n        consider:</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Charitable Purpose:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> DIFC and RAK ICC allow for\n        foundations with exclusive charitable purposes, which are not permitted under\n        ADGM regulations.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Dispute Resolution:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> DIFC allows foundation disputes to\n        be settled through arbitration, unlike ADGM and RAK ICC.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Minimum Capital:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> ADGM and RAK ICC require an initial\n        capital of US$100 (or equivalent), while DIFC does not.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Public Register:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> ADGM and DIFC maintain publicly\n        accessible foundation information, while RAK ICC does not.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 19px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Annual Filings:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> Only ADGM foundations may not be\n        required to file or audit accounts annually unless requested by authorities.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Key Documents and Officers</span></strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Charter:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> This document outlines the foundation\'s purpose,\n        objectives, initial assets, founder information, and duration. It must be\n        written in English and comply with relevant regulations.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">By-Laws:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> These internal regulations govern the foundation\'s\n        administration and management.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;;\"><span><span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Officers:</span></strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 96px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"><span>o<span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Founder:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> The individual or entity initiating the foundation\'s\n        establishment.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 96px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"><span>o<span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Registered Agent:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> A qualified professional licensed\n        by the chosen jurisdiction to facilitate incorporation.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 96px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"><span>o<span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Council:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> A governing body responsible for overseeing the\n        foundation\'s operations.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 0px 96px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"><span>o<span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Guardian (Optional):</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> An individual who supervises the\n        foundation\'s activities on behalf of beneficiaries, typically for minors or\n        incapacitated individuals.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 0px 0px 19px 96px; text-indent: -24px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"><span>o<span style=\"font: 9px &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n            </span></span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Beneficiaries:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> Individuals or entities designated\n        to receive benefits from the foundation\'s assets.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Tax Considerations</span></strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Aptos; margin: 19px 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Family\n        foundations used solely to manage personal assets for designated beneficiaries\n        are generally treated as fiscally transparent for corporate tax purposes in the\n        UAE. This means the foundation\'s income is not subject to separate taxation.\n        However, specific conditions must be met for this treatment to apply. It is\n        recommended to consult with a tax professional for detailed guidance.</span></p>\n\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Disclaimer:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"> This article provides general information and does not constitute legal\n    advice. To seek personalized legal counsel tailored to your specific\n    circumstances, Growbal encourages you to contact <a>legal experts</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Aptos;\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">.</span>\n</p>',_binary '',_binary '\0','string','Establishing a Foundation in the UAE: A Legal Guide',2518,1,'2024-07-08 15:47:00.000000','This guide provides an overview of the legal framework surrounding foundations in the United Arab Emirates (UAE), specifically tailored for individuals considering this option for wealth management and succession planning.','Foundation','OHLLP',2517,'https://staging.growbal.net/agent/W5LRSoX3'),(17,'string','2024-07-08 15:18:08.510000','<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">The United Arab Emirates (UAE) has established a comprehensive legal framework specifically designed to support and regulate family-owned businesses. This legislation, Federal Decree Law No. 37 of 2022 Concerning Family Businesses (the \"Law\"), came into effect in January 2023.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Rationale and Objectives</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: norm