color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Newly established family businesses.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; font-size: 10pt;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 0pt 0px; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Family businesses located within free zones.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; font-size: 10pt;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 0pt 0px 14pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Family businesses operating in individual emirates, except where local legislation already governs such businesses (in which case, the Law may apply to non-regulated areas).</span></strong></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">The Law excludes joint-stock companies and partnerships from its scope.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Registration Requirements</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Family businesses are required to register with a unified Family Business Register established by the Ministry of Economy. This registration process may be coordinated with relevant local authorities depending on the Emirate or free zone where the business operates.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Family Charter</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">In addition to the standard Memorandum of Association (MoA), family businesses must create a Family Charter. This document outlines the governance structure for managing family involvement in the business and establishes guidelines for the family\'s relationship with the company. The Family Charter must be deposited within the Register. In the event of a conflict between the MoA and the Family Charter, the MoA provisions prevail.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Share Classes</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">The Law allows family businesses to issue two distinct classes of shares:</span></strong></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 2rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-inline-start: 48px; font-size: 20px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; font-size: 10pt;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal; font-family: Raleway;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Share (A):</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\"> Provides voting rights and entitlement to company profits.</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans Symbols&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; font-size: 10pt;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 0pt 0px 14pt; line-height: 1.2;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal; font-family: Raleway;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Share (B):</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\"> Grants exclusive rights to profits without voting privileges.</span></strong></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">The Law allows a family business, with majority shareholder approval, to repurchase up to 30% of its own share capital in specific situations, such as capital reduction or purchasing shares from a departing member.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Management Structure</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">The MoA designates the management structure for a family business. In the absence of such provisions, partners holding at least 51% of the shares can appoint a director. Directors can be individuals or legal entities, although at least one director must be a natural person if there\'s more than one appointed.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">For family businesses established as limited liability companies, the MoA may specify the formation of a Board of Directors (BOD). The MoA will govern the rules, composition, and powers of the BOD, including terms of membership, compensation, appointment/removal procedures, and decision-making mechanisms. The BOD will appoint a Chairperson who acts as the representative but does not have a casting vote.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Dispute Resolution</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">The Law empowers family businesses to choose their preferred method for resolving disputes. Options include a dedicated Family Business Dispute Resolution Committee in each Emirate, the courts within financial free zones, or arbitration.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">Incentives and Support</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.2; font-size: 20px;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-f20500ac-7fff-087e-3c72-636bd789abac\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: Raleway; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;\">The Law creates a supportive environment for family businesses and family offices to establish themselves in the UAE. Additionally, family businesses may be eligible for occasional incentives and concessions at the discretion of the UAE Cabinet.</span></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; margin: 14pt 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0p