INSERT INTO `steps` VALUES (7,_binary '','In the initial phase of the Antigua and Barbuda Citizenship by Investment process, your application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This comprehensive evaluation aims to ensure that all aspects of your application align with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',23),(8,_binary '','Subsequently, investors delve into the paperwork, assembling crucial documents required for the Citizenship by Investment program. These include a valid passport, birth certificate, police clearance, financial documents, employment/ business documents, ID, proof of address and evidence of the investment made. This step is pivotal in preparing a comprehensive application package.','3-5 Weeks',1,'Preparation of Documents','Preparation of Documents',23),(9,_binary '','The compiled documents undergo a meticulous due diligence check by the Antigua and Barbuda CBI unit. This ensures compliance with legal standards, making it a crucial stage in the CBI program. The goal is to determine the applicants\' suitability for citizenship based on the authenticity and legality of their provided information.','3 Months',1,'Due Diligence Check','Due Diligence Check',23),(10,_binary '','Once approved, applicants must provide evidence of their investment to obtain the Antigua and Barbuda passport. It\'s essential to complete the investment within a 30-day window, streamlining the process and ensuring a swift transition to full citizenship.','30 Days',1,'Approval and Investment','Approval and Investment',23),(11,_binary '','Approved investors and their adult family members take the oath of allegiance as a commitment to their adopted nation. This commitment can be fulfilled through videoconferencing, consulate sessions, or in-person ceremonies in Antigua and Barbuda. Once the oath is taken, successful applicants are granted citizenship, and their legal status is sealed with the issuance of an Antigua and Barbuda passport. This passport signifies their official membership in the country, granting them the associated privileges of citizenship.','4 Weeks',1,'Passports and Oath of Allegiance','Passports and Oath of Allegiance',23),(12,_binary '\0','In the initial phase of the Antigua and Barbuda Citizenship by Investment process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This comprehensive evaluation aims to ensure that all aspects of their application align with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.\n','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',23),(13,_binary '\0','Subsequently, investors delve into the paperwork, assembling crucial documents required for the Citizenship by Investment program. These include a valid passport, birth certificate, police clearance, financial documents, employment or business documents, ID, proof of address and evidence of the investment made. This step is pivotal in preparing a comprehensive application package.','3-5 Weeks',1,'Documents Preparation ','Documents Preparation ',23),(14,_binary '\0','The compiled documents undergo a meticulous due diligence check by the Antigua and Barbuda CBI unit. This ensures compliance with legal standards, making it a crucial stage in the CBI program. The goal is to determine the applicants\' suitability for citizenship based on the authenticity and legality of their provided information.\n','3 Months',1,'Due Diligence Check ','Due Diligence Check ',23),(15,_binary '\0','Once approved, applicants must provide evidence of their investment to obtain the Antigua and Barbuda passport. It\'s essential to complete the investment within a 30-day window, streamlining the process and ensuring a swift transition to full citizenship.','30 Days',1,'Approval and Investment','Approval and Investment',23),(16,_binary '\0','Approved investors and their adult family members take the oath of allegiance as a commitment to their adopted nation. This commitment can be fulfilled through videoconferencing, consulate sessions, or in-person ceremonies in Antigua and Barbuda. Once the oath is taken, successful applicants are granted citizenship, and their legal status is sealed with the issuance of an Antigua and Barbuda passport. This passport signifies their official membership in the country, granting them the associated privileges of citizenship.','4 Weeks',1,'Passports and Oath of Allegiance','Passports and Oath of Allegiance',23),(17,_binary '\0','In the initial phase of the Dominica Citizenship by Investment process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This comprehensive evaluation aims to ensure that all aspects of their application align with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.\n','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',24),(18,_binary '\0','Subsequently, investors delve into the paperwork, assembling crucial documents required for the Dominica Citizenship by Investment (CBI) program. These include fingerprint and photograph verification form, medical questionnaire and certificate, copies of all passports held, birth certificate, police record for applicants over 16 years old.\n','2-4 Weeks',1,'Documents Preparation ','Documents Preparation ',24),(19,_binary '\0','After collecting all documents for everyone on the application, Dominica\'s authorities carefully review them. They check for any problems or reasons to reject the application, making sure each applicant meets the necessary requirements. This helps maintain a straightforward and transparent evaluation process.','3-6 Months',1,'Due Diligence Check and Application Processing','Due Diligence Check and Application Processing',24),(20,_binary '\0','Once approved, applicants must provide evidence of their investment to obtain the Dominica passport. It\'s essential to complete the investment within a 30-day window, streamlining the process and ensuring a swift transition to full citizenship.','30 Days',1,'Approval and Investment','Approval and Investment',24),(21,_binary '\0','The CBI unit starts preparing the documents once the investment has been made. Dominica passports will be dispatched to each member of the application within a timeframe of 4 weeks.','4 Weeks',1,'Passport Granted','Passport Granted',24),(22,_binary '\0','In the initial phase of the Egypt Citizenship Investment process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This comprehensive evaluation aims to ensure that all aspects of their application align with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.','1 Day',1,'Primary Due diligence','Primary Due diligence',25),(23,_binary '\0','Subsequently, investors delve into the paperwork, assembling crucial documents required for the Egypt Citizenship by Investment program. These include passport copies, birth certificate, four passport photos, a receipt of payment of the USD10,000 government fee, a certificate of no criminal record, and a medical examination report.','2 Weeks',1,'Documents Preparation and Application','Documents Preparation and Application',25),(24,_binary '\0','Investors\' documents go through two stages of review. In the first three months, the applicant is examined using the databases of the Egyptian security authorities.','3 Months',1,'First Due Diligence','First Due Diligence',25),(25,_binary '\0','Following the initial background check, the applicant is granted a 6-month residence permit. During this period, the participant is supposed to travel to Egypt and make the investment.','',1,'Temporary Residence Permit','Temporary Residence Permit',25),(26,_binary '\0','Once the investment requirement is met, the program\'s department carries out another background check. If the candidate is approved, the department suggests the investor to the Prime Minister of Egypt, who then signs the naturalization documents.','3 Months',1,'Second Due Diligence','Second Due Diligence',25),(27,_binary '\0','The investor receives the naturalization certificate along with their passport.','',1,'Citizenship Obtainment ','Citizenship Obtainment ',25),(28,_binary '\0','In the initial phase of the St. Kitts and Nevis Citizenship by Investment process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This comprehensive evaluation aims to ensure that all aspects of their application align with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',26),(29,_binary '\0','Investors gather important documents needed for the Citizenship by Investment program. These papers include passports, birth and marriage certificates and bank statements.','2-4 Weeks',1,'Documents Preparation','Documents Preparation',26),(30,_binary '\0','Once all documents have been reviewed, everything is sent to the government of St. Kitts & Nevis for a due diligence check, to make sure everything is in order. This step is necessary for everyone who is 16 years old or older. It helps ensure that those applying for the Citizenship by Investment program meet the required standards and are eligible for the benefits it offers.','4 Months',1,'Due Diligence Check','Due Diligence Check',26),(31,_binary '\0','Once approved by St. Kitts & Nevis, the applicant is required to make the obligatory investment of their choice within 90 days. Purchasing real estate that qualifies or contributing to the Sustainable Development Fund is required before the process is finalized.','90 Days',1,'Approval and Investment','Approval and Investment',26),(32,_binary '\0','At this point, passports are sent to each individual in the application within 4 weeks after the investment is complete. Now, applicants and their families can consider themselves citizens of St. Kitts & Nevis.','4 Weeks',1,'Passports and Oath of Allegiance','Passports and Oath of Allegiance',26),(33,_binary '\0','In the initial phase of the St. Lucia Citizenship by Investment process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This comprehensive evaluation aims to ensure that all aspects of their application align with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',27),(34,_binary '\0','Investors gather important documents needed for the St. Lucia Citizenship by Investment program. These papers include passports, certificates, bank statements and other personal and financial reports.','2-5 Weeks',1,'Documents Preparation','Documents Preparation',27),(35,_binary '\0','Once all documents have been reviewed, everything is sent to the government of St. Lucia for a due diligence check, to make sure everything is in order. An interview is a part of Due Diligence. The main applicant can pass it in person or online. The procedure is in english.','3-5 Months',1,'Due Diligence Check','Due Diligence Check',27),(36,_binary '\0','Once approved by St. Lucia, the applicant is required to make the obligatory investment of their choice within 90 days. Transferring the required amount to the state fund, buying bonds or real estate, or investing in a business are required before the process is finalized.','90 Days',1,'Approval and Investment','Approval and Investment',27),(37,_binary '\0','Once the investment is complete, the St. Lucia passports will be in process. At this point, it is a requirement to send in an oath of allegiance and birth certificates for all applicants. In no more than 4 weeks, passports should be received by each member of the application.','4 Weeks',1,'Passports and Oath of Allegiance','Passports and Oath of Allegiance',27),(38,_binary '\0','In the first step of the Grenada citizenship by investment program, our experienced service providers at Growbal conduct a pre-approval review of the investors application. This evaluation is designed to align all aspects of their submission with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',28),(39,_binary '\0','Investors gather required documents, including personal documents and financial reports, passports, certificates and bank statements. These documents will be sent to the Grenada CBI unit.','2-4 Weeks',1,'Documents Preparation','Documents Preparation ',28),(40,_binary '\0','The Grenada CBI unit starts the Due Diligence check which will take about 2 to 6 months. An interview is a part of the process, which consists of answering the questionnaires.','3-6 Months',1,'Due Diligence and Application Processing','Due Diligence and Application Processing',28),(41,_binary '\0','Once the application is approved, the applicant needs to make the chosen investment within 30 days.','1 Month',1,'Approval and Investment','Approval and Investment',28),(42,_binary '\0','After completing the investment, passports will be sent to each individual in the application in just 4 weeks.','4 Weeks',1,'Passport Granted','Passport Granted',28),(43,_binary '\0','In the initial step of the Malta Citizenship by Investment process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This phase will determine whether the Maltese authorities will approve their application.','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',29),(44,_binary '\0','A police clearance certificate will need to be obtained for every member of an application over 12 years of age. This involves checking data in Interpol and Europol databases. Subsequently, applicants can proceed to obtain a residence permit, granted to everyone above 18 years old with proper due diligence documentation, a real estate agreement and medical insurance coverage.','3 Weeks',1,'Residence Permit','Residence Permit',29),(45,_binary '\0','The eligibility test must be conducted within 12 months from the residence permit card receipt. The Minister responsible for matters relating to citizenship approves or rejects applications. Successfully passing this test unlocks the opportunity to apply for citizenship.','4-5 months',1,'Eligibility Test and Approval','Eligibility Test and Approval',29),(46,_binary '\0','To apply for citizenship within 1 or 3 years, documents must be filled out and apostilled. Additionally, updated police clearance certificates are required for every applicant over 12 years old included in the application.','1-3 Years after the residence permit',1,'Citizenship Application','Citizenship Application',29),(47,_binary '\0','The governments approval will be submitted in writing. When approved, applicants have to fulfill all conditions within 4 months, invest a minimum of EUR 600,000 after 36 months with a residence permit or EUR 750,000 after 12 months with a residence permit. Also, they need to prove their residence in Malta.','4 Months',1,'Approval and Investment Fulfillment','Approval and Investment Fulfillment',29),(48,_binary '\0','All applicants above the age of 6 collect their passports in person at the Malta Passport Department.','2 Months',1,'Receiving a Passport ','Receiving a Passport ',29),(49,_binary '\0','In the first step of the Austria citizenship by investment program, our experienced service providers at Growbal conduct a pre-approval review of the investors application. This evaluation is designed to align all aspects of their submission with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',30),(50,_binary '\0','Investors will be guided on potential investment options in the Austrian economy and will be advised on possible ways to invest, ensuring the best solution that aligns with their goals. Investors also gather required documents, which will be sent to the Government of Austria after the citizenship application has been approved.\n','3-6 Months',1,'Documents Preparation and Investment Selection','Documents Preparation and Investment Selection',30),(51,_binary '\0','Applicants will be assisted in the process of making a contribution in the selected form of investment, as well as preparing and submitting the application for Austrian citizenship. ','6-24 Months',1,'Investment and Citizenship Application','Investment and Citizenship Application',30),(52,_binary '\0','Application processing time differs depending on each individual case. The average time frame is 24 to 36 months. Decision on granting citizenship is made exclusively by the Austrian Government. Once the application is approved, investors can apply for a passport immediately afterwards, which is granted within a few days.','24-36 Months',1,'Approval and Obtaining Austrian Citizenship','Approval and Obtaining Austrian Citizenship',30),(53,_binary '\0','In the initial phase of the Portugal Golden Visa process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This helps save time and lowers the chances of rejection.','1 Day',1,'Due Diligence Check','Due Diligence Check',31),(54,_binary '\0','The main applicant obtains a unique nine-digit number, Nmero de Identificao Fiscal (NIF), at the local Tax and Customs Authority office. Similarly, the applicant sets up a bank account with a trusted institution in Portugal, following a straightforward process like anywhere else in the world. investors will need documents proving income, home address and identification for both procedures.','1 Month',1,'Set Up a Portuguese Bank Account and Tax Number','Set Up a Portuguese Bank Account and Tax Number',31),(55,_binary '\0','The applicants should choose their desired investment, whether it be investment fund units, starting a business, or investing in arts, culture, and research.','2-3 Weeks',1,'Investment Selection','Investment Selection',31),(56,_binary '\0','The applicants gather necessary documents and collaborate with their agent to organize them, which may include translating. E-copies are then sent to the Portuguese Immigration Office for review.','5-6 Months',1,'Document Submission','Document Submission',31),(57,_binary '\0','After approval, applicants and their families must visit Portugal to provide fingerprints and original documents. This is necessary for obtaining a residence permit card and all members of an application must be present in person.','1-2 Weeks',1,'Fingerprinting ','Fingerprinting ',31),(58,_binary '\0','Once the applicants submit their application, it may take 6 to 8 months to receive their residence permit card. Initially valid for one year, it can be renewed for up to five years. With this card, they can freely live and work in Portugal, enjoying the same benefits as other Portuguese citizens and residents.','6-8 Months',1,'Getting The Residence Permit Cards','Getting The Residence Permit Cards',31),(59,_binary '\0','In the initial phase of the Spain Golden Visa process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This helps save time and lowers the chances of rejection.','1 Day',1,'Due Diligence Check ','Due Diligence Check ',32),(60,_binary '\0','This stage may take a few months and involves choosing the right investment. applicants need to organize everything to complete the investment. A lawyer, acting on their behalf, will then get a taxpayer number for them and prepare the necessary investment documents.','1-4 Months',1,'Investment Completion','Investment Completion',32),(61,_binary '\0','After completing the investment transaction, applicants must visit Spain using a tourist or another relevant visa. All required documents will be prepared and translated if needed before submitting the application. Upon submission, applicants and their family members must be in the country to undergo fingerprinting by the police.','3-5 Weeks',1,'Application Submission','Application Submission',32),(62,_binary '\0','Upon approval, applicants can collect their residence permit cards in person. Initially valid for two years, they must revisit Spain for renewal after this period, with the possibility of extending the validity to five years at that time.','20 Days',1,'Approval and Residence Permit Cards','Approval and Residence Permit Cards',32),(63,_binary '\0','In the initial step of the Greece Golden Visa process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This comprehensive evaluation aims to ensure that all aspects of their application align with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.','1 Day',1,'Due Diligence Check','Due Diligence Check',33),(64,_binary '\0','If real estate is the selected investment, our service providers will help applicants in locating a suitable property, opening a Greek bank account, and obtaining a taxpayer number. For other investment types, our service providers will ensure all required transaction prerequisites are met and assist the investor in submitting the investment amount.','2 Months',1,'Investment Completion','Investment Completion',33),(65,_binary '\0','After completing the investment, applicants will be assisted in preparing and translating essential documents. Medical insurance is required for each person listed on the application and all documents are then submitted to the Ministry of Immigration for review. Upon approval, applicants and their family members must submit fingerprints before obtaining the residence permit card.','2 Months',1,'Application Submission','Application Submission',33),(66,_binary '\0','The residence cards will be issued 4-6 weeks after the biometrics. applicants can collect the cards at the government office, or they can be couriered to the chosen address.','1-2 Months',1,'Approval and Residence Permit Cards','Approval and Residence Permit Cards',33),(67,_binary '\0','In the initial step of the UAE Golden Visa process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This initial check helps to find possible issues and raise the chances of getting a visa.','1 Day',1,'Due Diligence Check','Due Diligence Check',34),(68,_binary '\0','Applicants will get help in preparing and translating essential documents to submit them to the government. To have an opportunity to explore the properties to buy, pass medical checkup and apply for a golden visa in the UAE, they will receive a 6-month multiple-entry visa. ','5-7 Weeks',1,'Documents preparation','Documents preparation',34),(69,_binary '\0','Applicants and their family members undergo a medical checkup in a UAE clinic in order to be tested for dangerous infectious diseases and a health status certificate.','1-5 Days',1,'Medical Checkup','Medical Checkup',34),(70,_binary '\0','Applicants apply for the visa and give biometrics to the General Directorate of Residency and Foreigners Affairs. Once the application is approved, they will get their residence visa.','30 Days',1,'Getting the UAE Residence Visa','Getting the UAE Residence Visa',34),(71,_binary '\0','In the initial step of the Cyprus permanent residence process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This initial check helps to find possible issues and raise the chances of getting a visa.','1 Day',1,'Due Diligence Check','Due Diligence Check',35),(72,_binary '\0','Applicants will be assisted in collecting translated and apostille documents, getting medical insurance and concluding a real estate lease agreement. The documents include originals and copies of valid passports, a biography, a confirmation of investment, a declaration confirming an annual income of at least EUR 50,000, proof of a permanent address in Cyprus and birth and marriage certificates.\n','2 Weeks',1,'Documents Preparation','Documents Preparation',35),(73,_binary '\0','Applicants need to complete the investment condition by transferring funds to a local bank account. The documents will be submitted to the Department of Lands and Surveys of Cyprus, including an application to reduce the VAT rate to 5%.','3-5 Weeks',1,'Fulfillment of Investment Conditions and Application','Fulfillment of Investment Conditions and Application',35),(74,_binary '\0','The decision typically takes around 2 months. Upon approval, applicants must visit Cyprus within one year to undergo biometrics and secure their permanent residence permit.','2 Months',1,'Application Processing and Obtaining Permanent Residence','Application Processing and Obtaining Permanent Residence',35),(75,_binary '\0','In the initial step of EB-5 Investor Visa process, investors application undergoes a pre-approval review by our experienced service providers at Growbal. This comprehensive evaluation aims to ensure that all aspects of their application align with the specified requirements, optimizing its chances of acceptance.','1 Day',1,'Preliminary Due Diligence','Preliminary Due Diligence',36),(76,_binary '\0','Before applying for the visa, applicants need to transfer investments to the selected project. Meanwhile, the required documents need to be prepared and translated, including original papers and the copies will be certified with a notary.','2-3 Weeks',1,'Investment and Documents Preparation','Investment and Documents Preparation',36),(77,_binary '\0','In the third phase of the process, applicants will be accompanied to file an I-526E petition and to check all documents. If they are living outside the USA, they apply through the US Department of State using Form DS-260. If they are already in the USA under a different visa status, they apply to change their status to a conditional permanent resident using Form I-485.','',1,'Applying For The EB-5 Visa','Applying For The EB-5 Visa',36),(78,_binary '\0','The US Citizenship and Immigration Services USCIS will review applicants documents for an EB-5 Visa for 3 or 4 years. Once approved, they will receive a Conditional Green Card valid for 2 years. ','3-4 Years',1,'Processing Application and Conditional Green Card','Processing Application and Conditional Green Card',36),(79,_binary '\0','Within 90 days before the conditional green card expires, applicants must file Form I-829 to remove restrictions on obtaining permanent residency. This form proves that they have maintained their investment and fulfilled the necessary job creation requirements. Now, they are eligible to get a US Green Card.','',1,'File Form I-829 and Get US Green Card ','File Form I-829 and Get US Green Card ',36);
